\int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^\frac{T}{2}p(t)e^\frac{-j2πnt}{T}dt=
-A\int_{-\frac{T}{2}}^{-\frac{T}{4}}e^\frac{-j2πnt}{T}dt+A\int_{-\frac{T}{4}}^{\frac{T}{4}}e^\frac{-j2πnt}{T}dt-A\int_{\frac{T}{4}}^{\frac{T}{2}}e^\frac{-j2πnt}{T}dt=
-A\frac{e^{jn\frac{π}{2}}-e^{jπn}}{-j2πn}+A\frac{e^{-jn\frac{π}{2}}-e^{jn\frac{π}{2}}}{-j2πn}-A\frac{e^{jπn}-e^{jn\frac{π}{2}}}{-j2πn}=
A\frac{\sin\left(n\frac{π}{2}\right)}{n\pi}=A\frac{(-1)^n}{n\pi}
